A three-year-old boy has been accused of killing his mother by pushing her down
lift shaft in China by one of their neighbours
Xie Hong Feng was found dead after falling five floors down an empty elevator shaft in her apartment block in Ningbo City in China
Her neighbour and property manager Yang Shao told police the 45-year-old had been pushed by her toddler son
CCTV image inside the lift shows Ms Xie with her three-year-old son
